== User Manuals

=== Professor Guide
+ *Access:* Navigate to the application link (e.g., `127.0.0.1:5173`).
+ *Selection:* Select the time slots during which you are willing to host the class.
+ *Details:* Enter your name and the class title.
+ *Submission:* Click the "Submit" button.
+ *Save Links:* Bookmark the generated unique links provided on the confirmation screen.
+ *Review:* Navigate to the results page via your bookmarked link to view student availability.

